I did not go. My family was racked and rent asunder from the stress and politics. My Brother died horribly many years after his return. I died with him. I look for someone to blame and hold for justice and I only see us. The police actions continue with the same tired results. And, the money -making maggots defend America from their desks. My children will not go through the mess that was and is Vietnam. My family has paid enough of a price. I am grateful that there is a neutral forum for comment and thoughtful insights. There is hope for democracy. Thank you. 
